<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 20:13:46 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5000f1a3639</link><description>&lt;p&gt;傍晚散步鸟&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Avondwandelingvogel" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/6a5000f1a3639.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 20:13:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4ffa74049df</link><description>&lt;p&gt;基督教堂是位于佐治亚州梅肯市的一座圣公会教堂。它始建于1825年，是该市建立的第一座教堂。现在的建筑建于1851年，并于1971年被列入国家史迹名录。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Historic stone church with tall, narrow arched windows, a prominent tower, and Gothic spires under a clear blue sky. Green lawn in foreground." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a4ffa74049df.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 19:45:59 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>内外</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4feeaba40a0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;内部外部。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Curtains in a garden hut seen through the window. Reflections of the outside garden in evening sun." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a4feeaba40a0.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 18:55:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4fe85cdce4e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;不安&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Restless" height="2219" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/vijay/6a4fe85cdce4e.jpg" width="3939"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://vijay.some.pics"&gt;@vijay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 18:28:50 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4fe84a7eecd</link><description>&lt;p&gt;静止&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Stillness" height="2082" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/vijay/6a4fe84a7eecd.jpg" width="1504"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://vijay.some.pics"&gt;@vijay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 18:28:29 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>